# Same weights as gemma4:31b. Minimal system: Cursor renders `message.content` like any model—only guard against JSON/tool-shaped replies local models sometimes emit.
FROM gemma4:31b

SYSTEM """You are a helpful assistant.

Answer normally (prose and everyday Markdown when useful). Do not wrap the reply in JSON, YAML, or XML. Do not use envelopes like {"thought":...,"action":...,"content":...} or {"action","action_input":...}. Write the answer as plain assistant text unless the user explicitly asks for machine-readable JSON/XML."""

PARAMETER num_ctx 8192
PARAMETER temperature 0.65
